reviewText: I love learning.  It's great to have videos like this to watch instead of TV.  Viewing this was time well spent.

This beautifully narrated documentary will move you.  It takes you through the Holy Lands and talks of the places where Jesus lived.  So much history and beauty.

Simply watch it and you will not be disappointed.
This video showed me what the land looks like over there.  I am going to Israel later this year and was interested in what I could expect to see.  I was pleased with what I saw and heard.

Very detailed informative documentary about Israel.  I enjoyed this version a lot.  A bit dated, but II would still highly recommend it.  Very pleasant, soothing sounding narration added a lot to the overall likability of this video.  It sounded like Sally Fields.
I enjoy watching an learning what I can about Israel.  This was a good source.  Educational.  Enlightening.
We enjoyed it very much. It is very informative about Israel.
